---
title: Creamy Leek & Potato Soup with Parmesan & Wholemeal Panini
description: What’s the best way to warm up over the cooler months? A bowl of comforting, homemade soup of course! This one’s super easy, all pulled together in one pot. Simmer hearty veggies in cream and stock for flavour and richness, and serve with crusty bread for dunking.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6620c163607542c1f3dcc31b-447fa1f0.jpeg
